      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/m/258eb7/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2017-05-01T07:36:15.576Z",
      "cooked": "<p>ti i propozon nje shoku te shkoni ne restorantin X.</p>\n<p>Ai te thote: Eshte restorant koti.</p>\n<p>ti  i pergjigjesh:</p>\n<p>Ndoshta. Po ti sa restorante ploti zoteron, dhe cilat jane ato?</p>\n<p><em>Key readings: Trip Advisor.</em></p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": 6,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 29406,
      "post_number": 14,
      "username": "Aquamarine",
      "name": "Aquamarine",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/aquamarine/{size}/11614_2.png",
      "created_at": "2017-05-01T07:48:20.868Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Pse shkrimtar eshte ki? Kush paska qene ne peshk? Une e dija perkthyes. Me eshte fiksu qe e kam pa njehere ne tv qe mori cmim ke cmimet kult, kishin bere nje atmosfere aty si cmimet oskar me zjarr e me pishtare… mbaj mend qe kur mori cmimin tha dhe fjalet e rastit: 'puna e perkthyesit eshte e veshtire, madje eshte nje kenge qe e kendoj bashke me gocen: olele kurrizi mi lale.'<br>\nDuhet te jete interesant ne shkrimtari. <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/slightly_smiling_face.png?v=5\" title=\":slightly_smiling_face:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slightly_smiling_face:\"></p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": null,
      "like_count": 0
    },
