      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/p/ecb155/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2017-05-01T11:52:46.023Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Po ç’ne qe shkruan BIRN per nje çmim, kur fare mire mund te shkruanin gazetat e tjera Gjembo,  po nejse mund ta kem une gabim, se dje po pija vere te perzier me rozmarine te thate, per ta bere sa me bio <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/yum.png?v=5\" title=\":yum:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":yum:\"></p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": 5,
      "like_count": 0
    },
